from pyspark.sql import functions as F
df_tweets_key = df_tweets_key.withColumn('Category',
    F.when((lower(col("description")).contains('news')) | (lower(col("user_screen_name")).contains('news')), 'news_outlet')\
    .when((lower(col("description")).like('%gov%') & (col('verified_user') == 'true'))|(lower(col("user_screen_name")).like('%gov%')& (col('verified_user') == 'true')), 'government_entities')\
    .when((lower(col("description")).like('%universit%'))|(lower(col("user_screen_name")).like('%universit%')), 'university')\
    .when((lower(col("description")).contains('school'))|(lower(col("user_screen_name")).contains('school')), 'school')\
    .when((lower(col("description")).like('%non-profit%'))|(lower(col("user_screen_name")).like('%non-profit%'))|(lower(col("user_screen_name")).contains('ngo'))|
                                                            (lower(col("description")).contains('ngo')),'non-profit organizations')\
    .when(((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('description')).contains('influencer')))|\
                                        ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('description')).contains('blog')))|\
                                         ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('description')).contains('vlog')))|\
                                         ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('description')).contains('tiktok')))|\
                                        ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('description')).contains('instagram')))|\
                                        ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('description')).contains('facebook')))|\
                                        ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('description')).contains('youtube')))|\
                                        ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('description')).contains('professor')))|\
                                        ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('description')).contains('teacher')))|\
                                          ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('user_screen_name')).contains('blog')))|\
                                           ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('user_screen_name')).contains('vlog')))|\
                                        ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('user_screen_name')).contains('tiktok')))|\
                                        ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('user_screen_name')).contains('instagram')))|\
                                        ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('user_screen_name')).contains('facebook')))|\
                                        ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('user_screen_name')).contains('youtube')))|\
                                    ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('user_screen_name')).contains('professor')))|\
                                    ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('user_screen_name')).contains('teacher')))|\
                                    ((col('followers_count')>50000) &(lower(col('user_screen_name')).contains('influencer'))),'social media influencer')\
    .otherwise('someone else'))
